---
title: Pan-Fried Lemon Chicken with Creamy Lentils & Veggies
description: You'll have every reason to feel smug when you serve up this dinner. The creamy sauce with lentils and chopped veggies is a perfect base for the juicy pan-fried chicken, coming together to make a meal that's nothing short of spectacular.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5d1d12480ae9db000d217fd5-6fb4a9ef.jpg
